snippet.title: NARUTO TO BORUTO: SHINOBI STRIKER - TGS Trailer | PS4, XB1, PC
snippet.description:
Ninjas! With your own set of skills and customized characters, get ready to fight your way to the top of the ninja league in NARUTO TO BORUTO: SHINOBI STRIKER!  

Plus, make sure your kunai are sharpened because we'll have a Beta Test coming soon! 

Preorder: http://amzn.to/2vsypwg
